WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(Default) {
color: #ffffffff;
font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
font-size: 020px;
text-shadow: #000000ff -2px 0px 2px, #000000ff 0px 2px 2px, #000000ff 0px -2px 2px, #000000ff 2px 0px 2px;
background-color: #00000000;
}

c0000000
00:00:00.420 --> 00:00:01.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're under siege?</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:01.840 --> 00:00:04.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how did
the Imperial army slip in?</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:04.130 --> 00:00:06.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] The palace
was caught off guard.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:06.670 --> 00:00:09.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've yet to fully grasp
the situation.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:12.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I know for sure
is that it's dire.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:13.430 --> 00:00:16.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin!
Go get the car ready, quickly!</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:19.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um!
Right away!</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:20.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Imperials at our doorstep.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:20.980 --> 00:00:23.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did they get past
the border without notice?</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:23.690 --> 00:00:24.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Listen...</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:24.610 --> 00:00:26.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm heading back
to the palace right now.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:26.490 --> 00:00:28.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever you do,
just stay safe!</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:28.990 --> 00:00:30.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
I have no other intentions.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:31.030 --> 00:00:32.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Why now?</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:32.530 --> 00:00:33.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Endure, Mother!</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:33.990 --> 00:00:34.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[running footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:35.080 --> 00:00:36.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:36.370 --> 00:00:37.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Ah?</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:37.580 --> 00:00:38.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Could it be?</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:38.870 --> 00:00:41.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They got wind of my absence
through an insider?</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:41.540 --> 00:00:43.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000021
00:00:43.170 --> 00:00:44.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is everything okay?</b></Default>

c0000022
00:00:44.460 --> 00:00:46.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You look really
shaken up, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:00:47.260 --> 00:00:48.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Did you do this?</b></Default>

c0000024
00:00:48.920 --> 00:00:50.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you send your army
after my mother?</b></Default>

c0000025
00:00:52.300 --> 00:00:53.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
What?</b></Default>

c0000026
00:00:53.470 --> 00:00:56.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going.
They need me at the palace.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:00:56.350 --> 00:00:57.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000028
00:00:57.270 --> 00:00:58.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look, Iska,</b></Default>

c0000029
00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:01.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to believe you had
nothing to do with any of this.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:02.060 --> 00:01:04.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, please,
stay here at the manor.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:04.570 --> 00:01:07.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not one step outside!</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:07.150 --> 00:01:08.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:08.820 --> 00:01:10.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Alice, what's going on?</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:11.530 --> 00:01:13.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Not a single step!</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:15.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I swear,
if you're betraying me, Iska,</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:15.410 --> 00:01:16.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll never forgive you!</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:16.830 --> 00:01:18.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, slow down!</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:18.290 --> 00:01:20.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't understand!</b></Default>

c0000039
00:01:20.250 --> 00:01:21.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Promise me.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:23.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000041
00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:57.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[SALINGER] How boring.
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000042
00:02:57.470 --> 00:03:00.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A coup hell bent
on assassinating the queen?</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:00.510 --> 00:03:02.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmph!
Hydra's handiwork, yet again.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:03.020 --> 00:03:04.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORNAKE]
You?</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:04.270 --> 00:03:06.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You Millavair's guard dog now?</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:06.100 --> 00:03:08.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:08.110 --> 00:03:10.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only one allowed to call
the queen by her name is me.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:11.940 --> 00:03:15.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thirty years later, and still
nothing's changed around here.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:16.070 --> 00:03:17.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR (YOUNG)]
Salinger!</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:17.200 --> 00:03:18.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me you didn't.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:18.780 --> 00:03:21.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me you didn't strike
the queen down, please!</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:22.290 --> 00:03:23.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:23.410 --> 00:03:25.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After everything
we've been through,</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:25.250 --> 00:03:27.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why would you betray me?</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:27.120 --> 00:03:29.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:29.170 --> 00:03:30.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER]
Milla.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:30.290 --> 00:03:32.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, Queen Millavair.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:33.010 --> 00:03:35.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As matriarch
of this burning nation,</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:38.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will you remain true
to your ideals?</b></Default>

c0000060
00:03:38.550 --> 00:03:40.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If so, defend them
with your life.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:03:41.050 --> 00:03:43.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000062
00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:45.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000063
00:03:45.890 --> 00:03:47.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gunshots]</b></Default>

c0000064
00:03:47.810 --> 00:03:49.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000065
00:03:49.810 --> 00:03:50.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MEI] [snickers]
Wow.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:03:50.900 --> 00:03:53.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pretty solid stuff
we've got here, huh, Names?</b></Default>

c0000067
00:03:55.570 --> 00:03:58.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, and you're 65 seconds
late to be in position.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:03:59.070 --> 00:04:00.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
They're heat-resistant.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:00.700 --> 00:04:02.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An attack like this
won't do much.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:02.990 --> 00:04:05.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which is why
I used incendiary bombs.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:06.500 --> 00:04:08.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hence the 65 seconds.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:08.540 --> 00:04:10.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:12.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh!</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:12.500 --> 00:04:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, where's Haim-zee?</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:14.710 --> 00:04:17.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Already en route
to the queen's palace.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:17.260 --> 00:04:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This'll be a walk in the park!</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:19.760 --> 00:04:21.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
That "walk in the park"</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:21.140 --> 00:04:24.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is infested with beasts
of the astral kind.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:24.100 --> 00:04:25.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't mess up.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:28.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>C'mon, you know I won't.
I live for this.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:28.440 --> 00:04:30.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, who's ready to hunt?</b></Default>

c0000082
00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:33.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'Cause I don't know about you,
but I'm just dying to see.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:04:33.400 --> 00:04:35.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The spawn of the Founder.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:04:36.610 --> 00:04:38.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[trembling]</b></Default>

c0000085
00:04:38.150 --> 00:04:40.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Soldiers?
In the palace?</b></Default>

c0000086
00:04:41.370 --> 00:04:42.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can't be.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:04:43.280 --> 00:04:44.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, Sisbell, wait.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:47.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I know this looks bad.
-Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:04:47.370 --> 00:04:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But please,
we knew absolutely nothing</b></Default>

c0000090
00:04:49.580 --> 00:04:51.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about this attack, I swear!</b></Default>

c0000091
00:04:51.960 --> 00:04:54.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know, how could you?</b></Default>

c0000092
00:04:54.420 --> 00:04:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been watching you
the entire time.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:04:57.590 --> 00:05:00.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, remember
what Elletear said to me?</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:01.050 --> 00:05:02.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So long as you stay
where you are,</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:02.970 --> 00:05:04.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Schwartz will return to you.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:07.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Basically, she wants us
to look the other way</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:07.310 --> 00:05:08.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while the palace is surrounded.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:08.890 --> 00:05:10.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
This doesn't make any sense!</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:10.980 --> 00:05:12.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why, sister?</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:12.730 --> 00:05:15.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Has everything until now
been nothing but a lie?</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:18.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why forsake your loyalty
to betray your home and people?</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:18.530 --> 00:05:19.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[glass shattering]
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:19.610 --> 00:05:20.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Get down.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:20.780 --> 00:05:22.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Jhin?
What's the meaning of this?</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:22.990 --> 00:05:24.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Windows aren't safe.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:24.280 --> 00:05:27.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those gunshots,
did you guys clock it?</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:27.290 --> 00:05:28.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like an Imperial rifle.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:05:29.040 --> 00:05:31.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TH Type-87.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:05:31.250 --> 00:05:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know I heard electricity.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:34.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sisbell gasps]</b></Default>

c0000111
00:05:34.130 --> 00:05:36.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're sitting ducks
in here, guys.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:05:36.130 --> 00:05:37.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nowhere is safe.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:05:37.880 --> 00:05:40.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No!
This can't be happening!</b></Default>

c0000114
00:05:40.630 --> 00:05:42.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, it is.
Quiet down.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:05:43.010 --> 00:05:44.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[JHIN] Boss.
-Right!</b></Default>

c0000116
00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:46.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Iska.
-[ISKA] Got it!</b></Default>

c0000117
00:05:46.640 --> 00:05:48.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000118
00:05:49.180 --> 00:05:50.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stand down!</b></Default>

c0000119
00:05:50.180 --> 00:05:51.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're Imperial soldiers!</b></Default>

c0000120
00:05:51.730 --> 00:05:52.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-Move, idiot!</b></Default>

c0000121
00:05:53.020 --> 00:05:54.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
They aren't from the army.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:05:56.230 --> 00:05:57.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000123
00:05:57.320 --> 00:05:59.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] No mercy,
not even for your own.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:05:59.650 --> 00:06:01.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told you,
they're not one of us.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:01.990 --> 00:06:03.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Ah?
-Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:05.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Assault rifle TH Type-87.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:06.030 --> 00:06:08.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Standard issue in the army,</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:08.200 --> 00:06:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but the center of gravity
is actually at the muzzle,</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:10.580 --> 00:06:12.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>making it tricky to shoot.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:12.290 --> 00:06:13.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These guys didn't know that.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:13.960 --> 00:06:16.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One look at their stance
and it's clear as day.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:16.750 --> 00:06:18.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NENE]
Iska! Jhin!</b></Default>

c0000133
00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Check it out.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:06:20.670 --> 00:06:22.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An astral crest!</b></Default>

c0000135
00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:24.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, do you see
what I'm talking about?</b></Default>

c0000136
00:06:25.180 --> 00:06:27.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're mages,
from the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:06:28.510 --> 00:06:30.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do any of these guys
look familiar to you?</b></Default>

c0000138
00:06:31.060 --> 00:06:32.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Jog your memory?</b></Default>

c0000139
00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:34.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, not really.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:06:34.730 --> 00:06:37.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, the actual army
attacks the palace</b></Default>

c0000141
00:06:37.190 --> 00:06:38.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>leaving us with the fakes?</b></Default>

c0000142
00:06:39.440 --> 00:06:40.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's going on?</b></Default>

c0000143
00:06:40.980 --> 00:06:43.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Disturbance coming from below!</b></Default>

c0000144
00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:45.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're already
inside the manor!</b></Default>

c0000145
00:06:45.610 --> 00:06:47.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Sisbell, where are the maids?</b></Default>

c0000146
00:06:47.200 --> 00:06:48.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[running footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000147
00:06:48.490 --> 00:06:49.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Their rooms are in the back,</b></Default>

c0000148
00:06:49.620 --> 00:06:51.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so they should be safe
for a little while!</b></Default>

c0000149
00:06:51.910 --> 00:06:53.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's not much time!</b></Default>

c0000150
00:06:53.290 --> 00:06:55.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Through the front door,
while we still can!</b></Default>

c0000151
00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:56.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOGETHER]
Gotcha!</b></Default>

c0000152
00:06:56.790 --> 00:06:58.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If anyone opens fire
from long range,</b></Default>

c0000153
00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:00.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll take care of them.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:07:00.300 --> 00:07:02.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone else is all you, Iska.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:07:02.840 --> 00:07:03.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Roger!</b></Default>

c0000156
00:07:03.970 --> 00:07:05.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bring it on.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:07:05.130 --> 00:07:06.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My blade's ready!</b></Default>

c0000158
00:07:08.050 --> 00:07:09.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000159
00:07:24.440 --> 00:07:25.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

c0000160
00:07:25.780 --> 00:07:27.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
Lady Sisbell!</b></Default>

c0000161
00:07:27.570 --> 00:07:29.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Glad to see you
made it out safely.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:07:29.580 --> 00:07:31.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am leader
of the Hydra family,</b></Default>

c0000163
00:07:31.540 --> 00:07:32.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Talisman.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:07:32.740 --> 00:07:34.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Wait a minute.
-[BOTH] Hm?</b></Default>

c0000165
00:07:34.200 --> 00:07:35.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you here?</b></Default>

c0000166
00:07:35.660 --> 00:07:37.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be calm, all is well now.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:07:37.620 --> 00:07:40.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not a hair on your head
will be harmed under my care.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:07:40.290 --> 00:07:42.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we must hurry,
lest the chaos spread.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:07:43.300 --> 00:07:45.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By that, you mean the uprising?</b></Default>

c0000170
00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:48.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Empire's goal
is painfully clear.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:07:48.390 --> 00:07:50.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take down the queen
and her allies.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:07:50.930 --> 00:07:54.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In fact, the queen warned
you are also in danger.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:07:54.310 --> 00:07:55.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said that?</b></Default>

c0000174
00:07:55.810 --> 00:07:57.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Indeed, she did.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:07:57.100 --> 00:07:59.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Time is of the essence,
Lady Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:07:59.310 --> 00:08:00.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come to my car.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:08:01.400 --> 00:08:02.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000178
00:08:02.730 --> 00:08:04.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000179
00:08:04.480 --> 00:08:05.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah?</b></Default>

c0000180
00:08:05.690 --> 00:08:07.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000181
00:08:07.700 --> 00:08:09.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have just
two questions for you.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:08:09.910 --> 00:08:11.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you really are
the head of Hydra,</b></Default>

c0000183
00:08:12.030 --> 00:08:14.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then that must mean
you have a good explanation</b></Default>

c0000184
00:08:14.330 --> 00:08:15.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:18.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN] If this is regarding
her belligerent attack,</b></Default>

c0000186
00:08:18.370 --> 00:08:21.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I already explained in the
inquisition with the queen.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:08:21.130 --> 00:08:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no way of knowing
why she did what she did.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:25.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I also find
the witnesses' accounts</b></Default>

c0000189
00:08:25.630 --> 00:08:27.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of her transformation doubtful.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:08:28.010 --> 00:08:29.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that right?</b></Default>

c0000191
00:08:29.180 --> 00:08:30.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One more question, then.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:08:31.550 --> 00:08:33.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN] As much
as I find this interrogation</b></Default>

c0000193
00:08:33.180 --> 00:08:34.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be ill-timed,</b></Default>

c0000194
00:08:34.260 --> 00:08:37.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll answer any questions
to prove my innocence.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:08:37.480 --> 00:08:39.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Idiot.
[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000196
00:08:39.190 --> 00:08:41.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are two suspects
behind the coup.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:08:41.690 --> 00:08:44.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Elletear and you.
-[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000198
00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:47.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang on, that can't be true,
he's innocent.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:08:47.740 --> 00:08:49.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right now,
the Imperial soldiers</b></Default>

c0000200
00:08:49.450 --> 00:08:51.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are actually at the palace.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:52.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By that logic,</b></Default>

c0000202
00:08:52.570 --> 00:08:54.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why would the manor
be under attack</b></Default>

c0000203
00:08:54.160 --> 00:08:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by astral mages
disguised as the army?</b></Default>

c0000204
00:08:56.580 --> 00:08:57.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000205
00:08:57.910 --> 00:09:00.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Coup's a coup,
but with Vichyssoise,</b></Default>

c0000206
00:09:00.170 --> 00:09:01.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was done out in the open.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:09:02.630 --> 00:09:04.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why bother
disguising themselves</b></Default>

c0000208
00:09:04.420 --> 00:09:06.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as the Imperial soldiers
this time?</b></Default>

c0000209
00:09:07.550 --> 00:09:09.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-[JHIN] Simple.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:09:09.170 --> 00:09:11.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Under the current
circumstances,</b></Default>

c0000211
00:09:11.390 --> 00:09:13.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everyone would assume
the Imperial army</b></Default>

c0000212
00:09:13.470 --> 00:09:15.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>kidnapped Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:09:15.220 --> 00:09:16.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that's not enough,</b></Default>

c0000214
00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:18.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the only one
who'd zero in on her,</b></Default>

c0000215
00:09:18.680 --> 00:09:21.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has to be the mastermind behind
the queen's assassination.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:09:22.020 --> 00:09:24.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all, if she returns
to the royal palace,</b></Default>

c0000217
00:09:24.770 --> 00:09:26.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she can find out
the true culprit.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:09:26.650 --> 00:09:28.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
Ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:09:28.280 --> 00:09:30.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unlike players
with reasons to revolt,</b></Default>

c0000220
00:09:30.740 --> 00:09:33.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>our family does not spurn
the regime.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:09:33.280 --> 00:09:35.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pick another bluff,
'cause I don't buy it.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:09:36.030 --> 00:09:38.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Zoas and Masked Lord
have nothing to do with this.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:09:38.750 --> 00:09:40.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
How can you be so sure?</b></Default>

c0000224
00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:42.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN] Because we went
toe-to-toe with him</b></Default>

c0000225
00:09:42.750 --> 00:09:44.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in Alsamira.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:09:44.540 --> 00:09:47.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And apparently,
Zoa's a radical faction</b></Default>

c0000227
00:09:47.500 --> 00:09:49.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just itching
to destroy the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:09:50.010 --> 00:09:51.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Meaning, there's no way</b></Default>

c0000229
00:09:51.090 --> 00:09:53.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he'd work with his enemies
to stage a coup.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:09:53.430 --> 00:09:56.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Assured confidence
on a conjecture.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:09:56.180 --> 00:09:57.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For you to believe his act,</b></Default>

c0000232
00:09:57.350 --> 00:09:59.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that man has played you
like a fiddle.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:09:59.350 --> 00:10:00.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scoffs]</b></Default>

c0000234
00:10:00.430 --> 00:10:02.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, say he was
working for the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:10:03.060 --> 00:10:05.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why not bribe us
and kill off Sisbell,</b></Default>

c0000236
00:10:05.310 --> 00:10:06.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>instead of going through
all the trouble</b></Default>

c0000237
00:10:06.900 --> 00:10:08.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only to let her go free?</b></Default>

c0000238
00:10:08.400 --> 00:10:09.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000239
00:10:09.740 --> 00:10:12.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zoa's innocent
as far as this coup goes.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:10:12.400 --> 00:10:14.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That leaves us
with only one descendant.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:10:15.070 --> 00:10:16.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000242
00:10:16.490 --> 00:10:18.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Hydra family
is behind everything.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:10:18.910 --> 00:10:21.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[hands clapping]
Bravo!</b></Default>

c0000244
00:10:21.330 --> 00:10:24.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A round of applause for
seeing through the deception!</b></Default>

c0000245
00:10:24.210 --> 00:10:26.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you even know
of the dubious Masked Lord!</b></Default>

c0000246
00:10:26.920 --> 00:10:28.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[snaps fingers]
Well, no matter,</b></Default>

c0000247
00:10:28.170 --> 00:10:30.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall simply
keep carrying on.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:10:30.260 --> 00:10:32.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only thing remaining
will be the Empire's gunpowder</b></Default>

c0000249
00:10:32.880 --> 00:10:34.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and bullet holes.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:10:34.340 --> 00:10:35.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lord Talisman?</b></Default>

c0000251
00:10:35.930 --> 00:10:37.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would you do this?</b></Default>

c0000252
00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:40.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because all of this
is necessary, my dear.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:42.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In order to reach
the core of this planet,</b></Default>

c0000254
00:10:42.560 --> 00:10:45.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-we need the strength
of the Empire. -[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000255
00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:47.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Join our ranks, Lady Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:10:48.020 --> 00:10:49.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lend us the power
of your spirit.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:10:49.900 --> 00:10:53.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And we will use it to unlock
the mysteries of this planet.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:10:53.400 --> 00:10:56.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
What are you talking about?</b></Default>

c0000259
00:10:56.570 --> 00:10:59.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN] Sadly, your
bodyguards will need to go.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:10:59.410 --> 00:11:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As much as I enjoy a crowd,
too many players in this game</b></Default>

c0000261
00:11:02.410 --> 00:11:03.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would be a turnoff.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:11:03.500 --> 00:11:06.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, I must ask
your guard dogs to leave.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:11:06.420 --> 00:11:07.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000264
00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:10.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
You seem surprised.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:13.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it because we used
your own trick against you?</b></Default>

c0000266
00:11:13.300 --> 00:11:14.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[beeping]</b></Default>

c0000267
00:11:14.380 --> 00:11:17.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, we can trip
an Imperial-made bomb.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:11:17.180 --> 00:11:18.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell, run!</b></Default>

c0000269
00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:20.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000270
00:11:20.430 --> 00:11:21.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Please be careful!</b></Default>

c0000271
00:11:21.810 --> 00:11:23.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His astral art is a wave-type!</b></Default>

c0000272
00:11:23.810 --> 00:11:25.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000273
00:11:25.890 --> 00:11:27.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000274
00:11:27.520 --> 00:11:30.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm, impressively done,
soldier.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:11:30.650 --> 00:11:32.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000276
00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:34.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Would love
to see you try and spin this</b></Default>

c0000277
00:11:34.440 --> 00:11:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the Empire after today.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:11:36.530 --> 00:11:37.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
There's no need for that,</b></Default>

c0000279
00:11:38.030 --> 00:11:39.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall burn everything down</b></Default>

c0000280
00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:41.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>using your Imperial explosives.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:11:41.620 --> 00:11:44.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Astral energy from my waves
will dissipate before long,</b></Default>

c0000282
00:11:44.960 --> 00:11:46.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>leaving nothing but the damage</b></Default>

c0000283
00:11:46.540 --> 00:11:47.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>caused by the Imperials.
[fingers snapping]</b></Default>

c0000284
00:11:47.790 --> 00:11:48.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[guns clicking]</b></Default>

c0000285
00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:51.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bring Lady Sisbell
to me unharmed.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:11:51.130 --> 00:11:52.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SOLDIERS]
Sir!</b></Default>

c0000287
00:11:52.340 --> 00:11:53.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, dear.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:11:53.760 --> 00:11:56.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Participating in such
barbaric acts of violence</b></Default>

c0000289
00:11:56.130 --> 00:11:58.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is far beneath my station.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:11:58.720 --> 00:12:00.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
You can't be serious.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:12:00.430 --> 00:12:02.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though we may be at odds.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:12:02.260 --> 00:12:04.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I assure you, I abhor violence.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:12:05.430 --> 00:12:06.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However though...</b></Default>

c0000294
00:12:06.940 --> 00:12:08.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"purification..."</b></Default>

c0000295
00:12:08.520 --> 00:12:11.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is far more palatable.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:12:11.110 --> 00:12:13.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see, all I desire</b></Default>

c0000297
00:12:13.150 --> 00:12:15.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is to purify
the planet's spirit.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:12:17.150 --> 00:12:18.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct shouting]</b></Default>

c0000299
00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:22.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosions]</b></Default>

c0000300
00:12:24.330 --> 00:12:26.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The citadel
for the astral spirits.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:12:26.790 --> 00:12:28.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hard to wrap my head
around the mechanisms</b></Default>

c0000302
00:12:28.710 --> 00:12:30.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>supporting this place.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:12:30.670 --> 00:12:32.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So much for the trek
to the queen's palace</b></Default>

c0000304
00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:34.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being a walk in the park.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:12:35.210 --> 00:12:36.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE 206A]
Word from the front, Miss Mei.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:39.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All entrances to the
queen's palace are sealed.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:12:39.300 --> 00:12:41.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our gunfire
isn't making a dent.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:12:41.220 --> 00:12:43.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks, Cappy,
but I already knew that.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:12:43.510 --> 00:12:46.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not taking a detour
to stretch my legs.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:12:46.230 --> 00:12:47.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE 206A]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000311
00:12:47.810 --> 00:12:49.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MEI]
So...</b></Default>

c0000312
00:12:49.230 --> 00:12:51.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's gonna be like that, huh?</b></Default>

c0000313
00:12:51.270 --> 00:12:52.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Cool.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:12:53.190 --> 00:12:54.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Erasure?</b></Default>

c0000315
00:12:54.400 --> 00:12:55.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Must be space-time based</b></Default>

c0000316
00:12:55.780 --> 00:12:57.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if everything
it touches disappears.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:12:57.740 --> 00:12:59.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Either way, it's vicious.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:12:59.700 --> 00:13:01.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nice to meet you, little miss.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:13:02.700 --> 00:13:04.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've been expecting you.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:13:04.580 --> 00:13:07.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Imperial soldiers
of the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:13:07.370 --> 00:13:09.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Greetings.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:13:09.080 --> 00:13:12.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name is
Kissing Zoa Nebulis the ninth.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:13:12.420 --> 00:13:13.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE 206A]
That's a purebred?</b></Default>

c0000324
00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:15.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE SOLDIER 206A]
They've finally showed up.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:13:16.550 --> 00:13:18.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MEI]
Well, it took you long enough.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:13:19.220 --> 00:13:20.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I was asleep.
-[scoffs]</b></Default>

c0000327
00:13:20.970 --> 00:13:22.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000328
00:13:22.930 --> 00:13:24.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, you were!</b></Default>

c0000329
00:13:24.430 --> 00:13:25.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're just a kid.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:13:25.760 --> 00:13:28.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should be tucked
in bed by now.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:13:28.310 --> 00:13:30.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why
you need to disappear.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:13:30.350 --> 00:13:32.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm still tired.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:13:32.270 --> 00:13:33.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Farewell forever.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:13:35.570 --> 00:13:36.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
Look.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:13:36.940 --> 00:13:39.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The flames swelling
under the stars.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:13:39.400 --> 00:13:42.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like a grand flower
blooming against firelight.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:13:42.870 --> 00:13:44.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Beautiful, yet bewitching.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:13:44.620 --> 00:13:46.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Cruel, yet fragile.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:13:46.660 --> 00:13:47.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pity.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:13:47.740 --> 00:13:49.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm terribly disappointed.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:13:50.500 --> 00:13:51.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
Why?</b></Default>

c0000342
00:13:51.870 --> 00:13:53.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We might not be
the audience you wanted,</b></Default>

c0000343
00:13:53.790 --> 00:13:56.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but give us some points
for at least showing up, yeah?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:13:57.000 --> 00:13:58.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
Surprises have been</b></Default>

c0000345
00:13:58.130 --> 00:13:59.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a recurring theme lately.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:13:59.840 --> 00:14:02.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This crimson flower was meant
to bloom in the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:14:02.930 --> 00:14:05.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And not on Sovereignty's soil.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:14:06.140 --> 00:14:07.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Truly discouraging.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:14:07.720 --> 00:14:08.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
Oh, cheer up!</b></Default>

c0000350
00:14:09.060 --> 00:14:12.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at it this way,
great minds think alike!</b></Default>

c0000351
00:14:12.100 --> 00:14:14.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, care to start?</b></Default>

c0000352
00:14:14.150 --> 00:14:15.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This might all go
a little easier</b></Default>

c0000353
00:14:15.900 --> 00:14:17.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if we knew each other's
names, stranger.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:14:17.770 --> 00:14:20.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
Ah, how rude.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:14:20.240 --> 00:14:21.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do forgive me.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:14:21.820 --> 00:14:22.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name is On.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:14:23.070 --> 00:14:25.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'm known
as the Masked Lord.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:27.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ooh, aren't you
the model gentleman?</b></Default>

c0000359
00:14:27.530 --> 00:14:29.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, my name is Risya.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:14:29.950 --> 00:14:31.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
The Disciple.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:14:31.500 --> 00:14:33.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, am I that famous?</b></Default>

c0000362
00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:34.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:14:34.500 --> 00:14:36.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)] A moment
of your time, if I may.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:14:36.380 --> 00:14:38.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a message to deliver
from the head of our family.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:14:40.130 --> 00:14:41.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
Go on.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:14:41.670 --> 00:14:43.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOGETHER]
First, I'd like to thank you.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:14:43.840 --> 00:14:45.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The fate
of this planet brought us</b></Default>

c0000368
00:14:45.430 --> 00:14:47.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a most remarkable guest,
you see.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:14:49.640 --> 00:14:51.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When the strength
of my legs faded</b></Default>

c0000370
00:14:51.730 --> 00:14:52.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>40 years ago,</b></Default>

c0000371
00:14:53.060 --> 00:14:55.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I smothered my dream
of ever being champion</b></Default>

c0000372
00:14:55.400 --> 00:14:57.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the battlefield.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:14:57.110 --> 00:14:59.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] The insurmountable
weight of that grief</b></Default>

c0000374
00:14:59.480 --> 00:15:02.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>consumed every waking
moment of my life.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:15:03.110 --> 00:15:05.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000376
00:15:05.660 --> 00:15:07.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000377
00:15:07.450 --> 00:15:09.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the fire burns
again tonight!</b></Default>

c0000378
00:15:09.790 --> 00:15:11.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And were it not
for you standing here,</b></Default>

c0000379
00:15:12.040 --> 00:15:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my ambitions
to destroy the Empire</b></Default>

c0000380
00:15:13.830 --> 00:15:16.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would have remained
a sweet fantasy!</b></Default>

c0000381
00:15:22.460 --> 00:15:24.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
Die, demon.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:15:25.720 --> 00:15:27.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY]
Mongrel.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:15:27.470 --> 00:15:29.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your sin runs deep.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:15:29.680 --> 00:15:30.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
What?</b></Default>

c0000385
00:15:30.850 --> 00:15:33.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] I am Zoa's
family head, Growley.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:15:33.890 --> 00:15:36.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I will take the measure
of what lies submerged</b></Default>

c0000387
00:15:36.230 --> 00:15:37.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in your mortal flesh.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:15:38.060 --> 00:15:40.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000389
00:15:40.320 --> 00:15:42.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's an escape doorway!</b></Default>

c0000390
00:15:42.150 --> 00:15:43.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can leave from here!</b></Default>

c0000391
00:15:44.530 --> 00:15:46.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN] A back door
to keep us under the radar?</b></Default>

c0000392
00:15:46.910 --> 00:15:49.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] Exactly.
I'll lead the way.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:15:52.410 --> 00:15:53.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000394
00:15:54.040 --> 00:15:55.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000395
00:15:55.370 --> 00:15:58.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, you said it was
an escape door,</b></Default>

c0000396
00:15:58.290 --> 00:15:59.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you really meant it.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:15:59.710 --> 00:16:01.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wish we had one of these
back at home.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:16:01.960 --> 00:16:04.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wish you two
would stop gawking and go.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:16:04.510 --> 00:16:06.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000400
00:16:06.180 --> 00:16:08.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you keep clinging
like a scaredy-cat,</b></Default>

c0000401
00:16:08.300 --> 00:16:10.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it'll be harder for me
to move when I need to.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:16:11.140 --> 00:16:13.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rude! Don't get
the wrong idea, mister!</b></Default>

c0000403
00:16:13.640 --> 00:16:15.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not scared,
it's just hard to see!</b></Default>

c0000404
00:16:16.600 --> 00:16:19.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Boss, Nene,
how's the ammo looking?</b></Default>

c0000405
00:16:19.400 --> 00:16:20.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:16:20.480 --> 00:16:23.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, I've got just about
half a charge left on my taser.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:16:23.610 --> 00:16:25.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Twelve bullets for me,
and we also have a grenade</b></Default>

c0000408
00:16:26.070 --> 00:16:27.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from one of the fake soldiers.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:16:27.950 --> 00:16:29.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not enough
for a war of attrition.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:16:30.450 --> 00:16:31.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000411
00:16:31.580 --> 00:16:32.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fall back!</b></Default>

c0000412
00:16:32.660 --> 00:16:34.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all scream]</b></Default>

c0000413
00:16:34.370 --> 00:16:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They even know about
the location of the tunnel?</b></Default>

c0000414
00:16:36.790 --> 00:16:37.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how?</b></Default>

c0000415
00:16:37.870 --> 00:16:39.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Keep running, I'll follow!</b></Default>

c0000416
00:16:39.960 --> 00:16:41.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
Another ice user?</b></Default>

c0000417
00:16:41.670 --> 00:16:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't good.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:16:42.840 --> 00:16:44.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way out
without a fight.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:16:45.840 --> 00:16:47.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000420
00:16:47.220 --> 00:16:49.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Mismis and Nene grunting]</b></Default>

c0000421
00:16:49.130 --> 00:16:51.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] That'll buy us
some time, I think.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:16:51.220 --> 00:16:52.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000423
00:16:52.510 --> 00:16:54.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL]
Winter Scenery.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:16:54.350 --> 00:16:55.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Great Snowy Ravine.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:16:55.890 --> 00:16:57.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all grunting]</b></Default>

c0000426
00:16:57.680 --> 00:17:01.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL] Do children not know
the line between ice and snow?</b></Default>

c0000427
00:17:01.560 --> 00:17:04.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then allow me the pleasure
to paint you a snowscape</b></Default>

c0000428
00:17:04.150 --> 00:17:05.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>right where you stand.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:17:06.610 --> 00:17:10.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, the illustrious
Lady Sisbell?</b></Default>

c0000430
00:17:11.070 --> 00:17:13.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How wonderful to make
your acquaintance.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:17:13.410 --> 00:17:15.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Charmed.
Who are you, anyway?</b></Default>

c0000432
00:17:15.830 --> 00:17:18.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Grugell,
the Midnight Sun Witch, right?</b></Default>

c0000433
00:17:18.250 --> 00:17:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL]
Oh, an Imperial soldier</b></Default>

c0000434
00:17:20.460 --> 00:17:22.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that knows of my name?</b></Default>

c0000435
00:17:22.380 --> 00:17:24.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was told that
the entire Fifth Division</b></Default>

c0000436
00:17:24.550 --> 00:17:25.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>had been wiped out by you.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:17:27.260 --> 00:17:28.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Annihilated.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:17:29.050 --> 00:17:31.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000439
00:17:32.590 --> 00:17:36.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here, the realm
of snow is mine to mold.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:17:36.220 --> 00:17:39.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pray tell, what chance do
descendants of the Founder have</b></Default>

c0000441
00:17:39.390 --> 00:17:41.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>against a Goddess?</b></Default>

c0000442
00:17:41.310 --> 00:17:42.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Punch it, Rin.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:44.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Up to 300!
-[car revving]</b></Default>

c0000444
00:17:44.310 --> 00:17:46.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What vehicle can go that fast?</b></Default>

c0000445
00:17:46.780 --> 00:17:49.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the Imperial army
really is invading,</b></Default>

c0000446
00:17:49.440 --> 00:17:51.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just how much damage
can they inflict?</b></Default>

c0000447
00:17:52.910 --> 00:17:54.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Minimal.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:17:54.160 --> 00:17:57.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If they did infiltrate it,
their numbers would tally...</b></Default>

c0000449
00:17:57.870 --> 00:17:59.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at most, a few dozen.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:17:59.710 --> 00:18:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only their firearms would've
passed through security.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:18:03.500 --> 00:18:04.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're right.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:18:04.590 --> 00:18:07.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, Sovereignty
can withstand an uprising.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:18:08.010 --> 00:18:10.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The royal family cannot.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:18:10.130 --> 00:18:13.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, even if there are
no civilian fatalities,</b></Default>

c0000455
00:18:13.470 --> 00:18:16.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if the queen falls,
so, too, does our nation.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:18:16.260 --> 00:18:17.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000457
00:18:18.890 --> 00:18:20.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
The palace.</b></Default>

c0000458
00:18:20.140 --> 00:18:21.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>On fire?</b></Default>

c0000459
00:18:21.730 --> 00:18:23.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How many weapons
were those lowlifes</b></Default>

c0000460
00:18:23.480 --> 00:18:25.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>able to smuggle
past the perimeter?</b></Default>

c0000461
00:18:26.320 --> 00:18:27.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
It can't be.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:18:29.150 --> 00:18:30.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Seems the Imperial army</b></Default>

c0000463
00:18:30.650 --> 00:18:32.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has crossed
the Sovereignty's border.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:18:32.950 --> 00:18:34.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
Everything is moving along.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:18:34.820 --> 00:18:37.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now we must wait
for the invasion.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:18:37.120 --> 00:18:39.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It must be at the hands
of the Imperial army</b></Default>

c0000467
00:18:39.450 --> 00:18:42.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Sovereignty loses
our beloved queen.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:18:42.410 --> 00:18:43.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Indeed.</b></Default>

c0000469
00:18:43.500 --> 00:18:46.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But your little sister
will be in our way, won't she?</b></Default>

c0000470
00:18:46.670 --> 00:18:48.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Such a shame, that.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:18:48.710 --> 00:18:51.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In terms of strength, she's
the most powerful of the Lou.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:18:52.670 --> 00:18:55.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If Alice focuses
on protecting the queen,</b></Default>

c0000473
00:18:55.470 --> 00:18:57.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Imperial army
won't stand a chance.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:18:58.680 --> 00:19:01.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, we must find a way
to lure Lady Alice</b></Default>

c0000475
00:19:01.180 --> 00:19:03.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from Nebulis' matriarch, yes?</b></Default>

c0000476
00:19:03.890 --> 00:19:05.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Talisman.</b></Default>

c0000477
00:19:05.100 --> 00:19:07.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm thinking of going
on a little getaway.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:19:07.810 --> 00:19:09.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To Lou's vacation house.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:19:09.940 --> 00:19:11.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Celebrating so soon?</b></Default>

c0000480
00:19:12.030 --> 00:19:14.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell cannot step foot
in the palace.</b></Default>

c0000481
00:19:14.280 --> 00:19:16.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'll figure out
who was behind the explosion</b></Default>

c0000482
00:19:16.370 --> 00:19:17.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the queen's hall.</b></Default>

c0000483
00:19:17.530 --> 00:19:19.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The house of Hydra
will be exiled.</b></Default>

c0000484
00:19:19.830 --> 00:19:21.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, I'll be the one
to take her to the manor.</b></Default>

c0000485
00:19:21.750 --> 00:19:24.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She will see that her
big sister is on her side.</b></Default>

c0000486
00:19:24.580 --> 00:19:27.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And be kept locked away
for just as long as we need.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:19:27.380 --> 00:19:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fascinating.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:19:28.590 --> 00:19:31.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And your self-indulgent action
will force Lady Alice</b></Default>

c0000489
00:19:31.460 --> 00:19:32.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to come to you,</b></Default>

c0000490
00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:34.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>following your trail
and pulling her</b></Default>

c0000491
00:19:34.720 --> 00:19:37.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the palace
so the queen's unprotected.</b></Default>

c0000492
00:19:37.340 --> 00:19:38.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Imagine it!</b></Default>

c0000493
00:19:38.970 --> 00:19:40.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alone and without a shield.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:19:40.600 --> 00:19:42.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lou the eighth is defenseless.</b></Default>

c0000495
00:19:42.770 --> 00:19:44.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lure Lady Alice
and Lady Sisbell</b></Default>

c0000496
00:19:44.730 --> 00:19:46.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the vacation house,</b></Default>

c0000497
00:19:46.310 --> 00:19:48.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so the Imperial army
can seize the moment</b></Default>

c0000498
00:19:48.360 --> 00:19:49.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to attack head-on.</b></Default>

c0000499
00:19:49.650 --> 00:19:52.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll be two birds
with one stone.</b></Default>

c0000500
00:19:52.230 --> 00:19:54.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]
Don't be silly!</b></Default>

c0000501
00:19:54.570 --> 00:19:57.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why settle with two
when you can have four?</b></Default>

c0000502
00:19:57.870 --> 00:19:59.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All in one move.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:19:59.740 --> 00:20:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One move to bring
this current regime</b></Default>

c0000504
00:20:01.700 --> 00:20:03.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>down to its knees.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:20:03.160 --> 00:20:05.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thus beginning a new election
for the next queen.</b></Default>

c0000506
00:20:06.500 --> 00:20:08.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose you'll be running
for Lou, Elletear?</b></Default>

c0000507
00:20:10.090 --> 00:20:11.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've grown tired
of this nation.</b></Default>

c0000508
00:20:12.050 --> 00:20:13.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Exhausted, really.</b></Default>

c0000509
00:20:13.590 --> 00:20:14.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But at the end of the day,</b></Default>

c0000510
00:20:14.800 --> 00:20:17.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to see it
burn to the ground.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:20:17.090 --> 00:20:18.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall leave its ashes to you.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:20:19.010 --> 00:20:20.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will consider it an honor.</b></Default>

c0000513
00:20:21.010 --> 00:20:24.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, allow me to escort you
to the Tower of Stars, my lady.</b></Default>

c0000514
00:20:25.180 --> 00:20:27.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Captain Ornake, come forth.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:20:27.350 --> 00:20:30.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a pleasure to meet you,
Princess Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:20:30.650 --> 00:20:31.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And who's this?</b></Default>

c0000517
00:20:31.940 --> 00:20:33.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The captain
of the intelligence corps,</b></Default>

c0000518
00:20:33.650 --> 00:20:35.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>selected by the house of Hydra.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:20:35.650 --> 00:20:38.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ornake is our finest assassin.</b></Default>

c0000520
00:20:38.240 --> 00:20:39.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My, how dependable!</b></Default>

c0000521
00:20:40.030 --> 00:20:42.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See, Lady Elletear
off to her destination.</b></Default>

c0000522
00:20:42.990 --> 00:20:44.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORNAKE]
Sir.</b></Default>

c0000523
00:20:44.240 --> 00:20:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Finished here?</b></Default>

c0000524
00:20:45.580 --> 00:20:48.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If so,
I've a vacation to attend.</b></Default>

c0000525
00:20:48.670 --> 00:20:49.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Carry on.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:20:49.830 --> 00:20:52.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And when our time approaches,
we will all be ready.</b></Default>

c0000527
00:20:54.920 --> 00:20:56.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000528
00:20:57.220 --> 00:20:59.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My Alice, Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000529
00:20:59.470 --> 00:21:01.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Mother.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:21:01.350 --> 00:21:04.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've all been blessed
with great astral spirits.</b></Default>

c0000531
00:21:04.310 --> 00:21:07.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Applauded since
the very day you were born.</b></Default>

c0000532
00:21:07.520 --> 00:21:09.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't have that luxury.</b></Default>

c0000533
00:21:09.480 --> 00:21:12.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you understand
what it's like to feel weak?</b></Default>

c0000534
00:21:13.480 --> 00:21:15.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, you don't.</b></Default>

c0000535
00:21:15.400 --> 00:21:17.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You probably think
this nation will never fall</b></Default>

c0000536
00:21:17.900 --> 00:21:19.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as long as you're leading it.</b></Default>

c0000537
00:21:20.490 --> 00:21:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, you see,</b></Default>

c0000538
00:21:21.700 --> 00:21:23.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's where you're wrong.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:21:24.370 --> 00:21:25.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's unfortunate, really.</b></Default>

c0000540
00:21:26.040 --> 00:21:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That strength
being your downfall.</b></Default>

c0000541
00:21:28.660 --> 00:21:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What good
are your spirits here?</b></Default>

c0000542
00:21:31.080 --> 00:21:34.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In this false paradise,
not even your gifts</b></Default>

c0000543
00:21:34.210 --> 00:21:35.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can save you now.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:21:36.670 --> 00:21:39.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tonight, this palace
will burn to ash.</b></Default>

c0000545
00:21:39.720 --> 00:21:42.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I'll be the one
to ignite those flames</b></Default>

c0000546
00:21:42.550 --> 00:21:44.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as the Witch of Catastrophe.</b></Default>

c0000547
00:21:45.310 --> 00:21:47.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A necessary price
that must be paid</b></Default>

c0000548
00:21:47.850 --> 00:21:50.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the name of a true paradise.</b></Default>

c0000549
00:21:50.310 --> 00:21:52.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] Keep the fire
extinguishing to a minimum.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:21:52.900 --> 00:21:55.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Use the extra manpower
to guard the tower.</b></Default>

c0000551
00:21:56.190 --> 00:21:57.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stand firm.</b></Default>

c0000552
00:21:57.730 --> 00:21:58.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ASTRAL FORCES]
Yes!</b></Default>

c0000553
00:21:58.940 --> 00:22:00.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[running footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000554
00:22:00.200 --> 00:22:01.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000555
00:22:02.660 --> 00:22:04.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly?</b></Default>

c0000556
00:22:04.160 --> 00:22:06.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do they really think
this will stop us?</b></Default>

c0000557
00:22:06.370 --> 00:22:07.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The fools.</b></Default>

c0000558
00:22:07.450 --> 00:22:09.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nebulis will not bow
to a ripple.</b></Default>

c0000559
00:22:10.040 --> 00:22:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a haven for all mages.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:22:12.080 --> 00:22:13.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JOHAIM]
"For all mages?"</b></Default>

c0000561
00:22:14.000 --> 00:22:15.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't make me laugh.</b></Default>

c0000562
00:22:17.460 --> 00:22:19.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000563
00:22:19.630 --> 00:22:21.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Queen Nebulis, I presume.</b></Default>

c0000564
00:22:22.720 --> 00:22:23.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000565
00:22:23.890 --> 00:22:25.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footfall]</b></Default>

c0000566
00:22:25.510 --> 00:22:27.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The name's Johaim.</b></Default>

c0000567
00:22:27.350 --> 00:22:29.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am the first seat
of the Saint Disciples.</b></Default>

c0000568
00:22:30.060 --> 00:22:31.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Disciple.</b></Default>

c0000569
00:22:31.980 --> 00:22:33.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[metal clanking]</b></Default>

c0000570
00:22:33.190 --> 00:22:35.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you seek forgiveness?</b></Default>

c0000571
00:22:35.270 --> 00:22:37.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Watch your mouth, lowlife.</b></Default>

c0000572
00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:40.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are now in the presence
of royalty.</b></Default>

c0000573
00:22:40.440 --> 00:22:42.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am Queen Nebulis.</b></Default>

c0000574
00:22:43.070 --> 00:22:45.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As the leader of Sovereignty,</b></Default>

c0000575
00:22:45.280 --> 00:22:47.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will vanquish you.</b></Default>

c0000576
00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:50.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JOHAIM]
You speak of a dream, Queen.</b></Default>

c0000577
00:22:50.660 --> 00:22:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This nation isn't a paradise.</b></Default>

c0000578
00:22:53.330 --> 00:22:55.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a delusion
wrapped in filthy lies.</b></Default>

c0000579
00:22:56.790 --> 00:22:58.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The new world's knocking.</b></Default>

c0000580
00:22:58.460 --> 00:23:00.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Time to answer.</b></Default>

